# Planning Optimizer

- Define scope, goals, non-goals, and success metrics before edits.
- Break work into phases with checklists and dependencies.
- Track risks, edge cases, and validation steps early.
- Execute in small batches, verify, and summarize changes.

## Example structure

```markdown
## Phase N — Title
### Checklist
- [ ] Task 1
- [ ] Task 2
```
